CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: For always doing this to you.

CONTENT: 調印は完了
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: All signed.

CONTENT: 以降 君たちの会社に 危害を加えないと誓う
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: Juro que no obstaculizaré más a su empresa.
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: I pledge I won't cause any harm to your company from now on.

CONTENT: ええ それじゃ
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Right. Bye, then.

CONTENT: 最初から決闘で奪えばよかった
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: Debería haberlo pedido en un duelo.
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: I should have dueled for it from the beginning.

CONTENT: 今さら泣きごと言っても⸺　会社はあげないわよ
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: No te daré la empresa por mucho que te quejes.
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: No amount of whining will get you this company now.

CONTENT: いや 君をだよ
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Not for that... but for your hand.

CONTENT: ホルダーになって君を守る
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: \"I'll become the Holder and protect you myself.\"

CONTENT: その一言が言えれば 俺も中に入れたのかな
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_SPANISH: Si hubiera dicho eso, ¿habría podido entrar?
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: If I'd only said those words, maybe you'd have let me in.

CONTENT: バカね
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Fool...

CONTENT: 今さらよ
CONTENT_TRANSLATION_ENGLISH: Too little, too late.
